Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.96,0:00:17.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,颯太
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.60,0:00:22.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.81,0:00:25.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,難得來度假
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:27.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,試試去約個女孩怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:30.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,誰都不會理像我這樣的人的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.91,0:00:32.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,還是睡午覺讓我感覺更安逸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.99,0:00:37.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,帽子？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:45.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.13,0:00:49.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.90,0:00:51.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.14,0:00:54.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.56,0:00:55.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.68,0:01:00.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,吶  和我一起玩遊戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.47,0:01:02.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,遊戲？
